    <body>
        <p>In your <xref href="dcpp_the_customization_css.dita">customization CSS</xref>, add the
      following CSS rule:</p>
        <codeblock outputclass="language-css">*[class ~= 'index/groups'] *[class ~= 'index/formatted-value'] {
    font-style:oblique;
    color:gray;
}</codeblock>
